** Blog App **

A simple full-stack blogging application built using the MERN stack.
Users can register, log in, create, edit, and delete their own blog posts. Public users can view all blogs and read individual posts. Session is maintained using JWT Authentification.

** Tech Stack **

Frontend: React (with Context API, React Router, Axios)
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB (Mongoose)
Auth: JWT-based authentication
Styling: CSS

** SetUp Instructions **

-- Clone repo
-- in blogs-BE create .env and put these fields:
DB_CONNECTION_SECRET and JWT_SECRET_KEY
-- run npm i or npm install to install node_modules
-- use npm start to run backend

-- now open folder blogs-FE
-- run npm i
-- enter command npm run dev to run the project
